00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:06,070
I can no longer think of him...

3
00:00:06,590 --> 00:00:09,980
as a target to destroy.

4
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:13,760
He acknowledged our efforts.

5
00:00:14,540 --> 00:00:16,390
He wasn't a bad guy.

6
00:00:18,610 --> 00:00:22,100
In that case, I no longer have...

7
00:00:23,050 --> 00:00:25,030
any reason to defeat him.

8
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:27,000
The King...

9
00:00:27,470 --> 00:00:30,000
The soldiers are not important.

10
00:00:30,310 --> 00:00:34,980
If the King waves his baton, the soldiers
will become demons if necessary.

